data.example-customizing-z80-assembly-colors#:
Let's customize the syntax highlighting for Klive Z80 Assembly:
Create a new file called kz80-asm.tokens.json in your Klive settings folder (~/Klive/ on macOS/Linux).
Add the following content:
{
